<br>
<br>
Wasting a half hour on a boat ride was not fun, you simply had no other option available.<br>
<br>
Coffining a guild out of a bad spot was not amusing.<br>
<br>
Stashing bodies outside Seb holding extra keys gave no additional dimension to the game.  It was simply bad design.<br>
<br>
<br>
